children = node

[cluster]

children = node

[cpu]

libs = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_matmul.so,/home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_visualizer.so,/home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_fftw.so

[gpu]

libs = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_ve_gpu.so
include = /home/bhbuilder/.local/share/bohrium/include

work_goup_size_2dx = 32
work_goup_size_2dy = 4
work_goup_size_3dx = 32
work_goup_size_3dy = 2
work_goup_size_3dz = 2
kernel = both
compile = async
children = cpu

[transitive_reduction]
type = filter
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_transitive_reduction.so
children = cpu

[pprint]

impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_pprint.so
children = cpu

[validate]
type = filter
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_validate.so
children = cpu

[range]
type = filter
impl = /home/bhbuilder/.local/lib/libbh_filter_range.so
children = cpu
